Song Search Web App

Description

This is a simple web application that allows users to search for songs and display relevant details like the song title, artist, album, and cover image.

Features

🔍 Search for songs dynamically

🎵 Displays song title, artist, album, and cover image

📜 Horizontal scrolling album list

🎨 Dark red and black stylish theme

Technologies Used

HTML for structure

CSS for styling

JavaScript for dynamic searching

File Structure

SongSearchApp/
│── index.html        # Main HTML file
│── css/
│   └── style.css     # Styling file
│── js/
│   └── index.js      # JavaScript logic
│── images/           # Folder for song images
└── db.json           # JSON file with song data

How to Use

Open index.html in a web browser.

Enter a song name in the search bar.

Click the "Search" button to find matching songs.

Scroll horizontally to explore albums.

Future Enhancements

🎶 Add audio playback functionality

🔗 Fetch songs from an external API

🌟 Improve UI with animations and effects

